# Title: APT29 2018 Phishing Campaign CommandLine Indicators
# Author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems), @41thexplorer
# Date: 2018-11-20
# Level: critical
# Description: Detects indicators of APT 29 (Cozy Bear) phishing-campaign as reported by mandiant
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.stealth, attack.t1218.011, detection.emerging-threats
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules-emerging-threats/2018/TA/APT29-CozyBear/proc_creation_win_apt_apt29_phishing_campaign_indicators.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Unlikely

CommandLine="*-noni -ep bypass $*" OR (CommandLine="*cyzfc.dat,*" CommandLine="*PointFunctionCall*")